public class EmbeddedMediaListPlayerComponent
extends EmbeddedMediaPlayerComponent
implements MediaListPlayerEventListener

Encapsulation of an embedded media list player.

This component extends the EmbeddedMediaPlayerComponent to incorporate a MediaListPlayer and an associated MediaList.
